				<td colspan="2"><span>Notice too, CHA Song (wozzitkalled), Niv's Harmonic AND Verses of Victory are all singing mod songs, not just PoV.  There is more to Amp than just adding resists on PoV (assuming you are not already mod capped at 4.2).
<br />

<br />
In MT group you will generally choose at least two from those four songs, depending on who the tank is (for example, ogre tank with unbuffed 60 cha aint capping it for DI without it, even with a shammy buff).  And more AC is always welcome ...
<br />

