Sure it helps (bragging rights) <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-13.gif" border="0" alt="LOL" hspace="2" />.  But not that usefull because it has a spell rune compent.  So when anyone gets hit with any spell the buff drops.  Rarely ever use anymore.  Do bring it out for trash mobs in tavci as well and VoV, rune, and pshamn.  Figure any boost you can give tanks that are doing flurry mobs that hit for 4.5k helps.  Couldn't stop laughing when we went in thier for the first time and raid wiped on first db con.  It did a wee bit more dps than anyone was expecting.
<br />

<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">VoV ? err.. Sing mod add absolutly nothing to VoV afaik. Yes its a singing song, realize that song have types for the game mechanic, not to know what mod will affect it. </span></blockquote> 
